location.fullValue: Silvercliff Plan, The Flats at Lupton Village

data.description: Welcome to this fantastic three-bedroom, three-bathroom home nestled on the renowned Coyote Creek Golf Course in Fort Lupton with great mountain views. With its picturesque patio overlooking the 14th hole on the course, this residence offers a rare opportunity to enjoy both luxury living and breathtaking views. Step inside and be greeted by an open-concept layout that creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. The living area features large windows that flood the space with natural light. The well-appointed kitchen suited with both functionality and a ton of space. Retreat to the generously sized bedrooms, each offering a tranquil space to unwind. The master suite, featuring expansive windows that frame the golf course views and an en-suite bathroom. The unfinished basement provides room for so many opportunities. Be sure to step outside onto the patio and immerse yourself in the beauty of the Coyote Creek Golf Course. This outdoor space is an idyllic setting to relax, entertain, and take in the stunning views. Whether you're enjoying a morning cup of coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends. Located in the highly sought-after Coyote Creek Golf Course community, this home offers a coveted lifestyle.
